### Chat API Examples with Conversation Context

@baseUrl = https://localhost:7029
@contentType = application/json

### 1. Create a new conversation session
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/session
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### 2. Start a conversation - First question: "What is 5 + 5?"
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "message": "What is 5 + 5?",
  "sessionId": "YOUR_SESSION_ID_HERE"
}

### 3. Continue the conversation - Follow-up question: "Add 2 to it"
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "message": "Add 2 to it",
  "sessionId": "YOUR_SESSION_ID_HERE"
}

### 4. Get conversation history
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/session/YOUR_SESSION_ID_HERE/history

### 5. Simple chat without session (no context)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "message": "What is the capital of France?"
}

### 6. Start a new conversation with specific model
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/session?model=llama3.2:latest

### 7. Clear conversation session
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/session/YOUR_SESSION_ID_HERE

### 8. Chat with custom model in existing session
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "message": "Tell me a joke",
  "sessionId": "YOUR_SESSION_ID_HERE",
  "model": "llama3.2:latest"
}
